#~ msgctxt "blurb"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "The hockey puck has become a globe. Amazon's Alexa-powered Echo Dot smart speaker is now round and there's even a version that can show you the time. Alexa has become the most bossed around bot on "
#~ "the internet. She plays music, turns on lights, makes phone calls, tells jokes, gives the weather, reads the news, orders toilet paper, and helps you feel less alone. Alexa will always be there for "
#~ "you, listening, ready to do your bidding, or sell you some new jeans because you asked her once how to lose weight."
