#~ "Enfin, elle déclare pouvoir partager ces informations avec un certain nombre de tiers."

#~ msgctxt "worst_case"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Let’s talk for a minute about Alexa itself. Amazon’s helpful artificial intelligence that’s built into everything from your Echo Dot smart speaker to your headphones to your thermostat comes with "
